            <p class="md:w-full max-w-[900px] pb-2 xl:py-4 border-gray-200 col-span-2">OpenPolicy was designed to bridge the gap between the people and the government. Currently, there isn't an official platform that allows citizens to voice their concerns, 
                vote, or engage with bills being passed. OpenPolicy changes that.   <br><br>
                The app provides a way for people to stay updated on government policies, track bills, and connect with representatives, all in one place.
