                    The goal was simple: give people a way to follow <strong>what’s happening in Parliament</strong> and <strong>have a say</strong> in the process. <br><br>
                    There was an existing app when I joined the project, but it had major usability issues. The design was cluttered, confusing, 
                    and didn’t fully support the app’s mission. My task was to <strong>completely redesign the experience</strong>
                    while keeping the core functionalities intact, making it more intuitive and accessible for users.
                </p>
