                <li class="flex flex-col items-start">
                    <span class="bg-black text-center flex justify-center items-center rounded-full w-[44px] xl:w-[44px] overflow-clip text-bold aspect-square text-white font-bold">1</span>
                    <strong class="text-base self-start mt-6 mb-2 font-bold">Redesigning Without a PRD</strong>
                    <span>When I stepped in, there was no Product Requirements Document (PRD), making it difficult to understand the full scope of the project. I had to reverse-engineer the previous app, speak with stakeholders, and map out the entire system myself.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex flex-col items-start">
                    <span class="bg-black text-center flex justify-center items-center rounded-full w-[44px] xl:w-[44px] overflow-clip text-bold aspect-square text-white font-bold">2</span>
